iStat Menus v4.1.0
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://bjango.com/mac/istatmenus/


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "iStat Menus v4.1.0.dmg" and Install the App.
- Open the Keygen app and generate the necessary license/serial information. Enter (copy-paste) the generated information in the app. 
- Enjoy.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update the app. You have been warned.
- If it says that the app is damaged. Then go to the System Preferences > Security and Privacy > General > Allow apps downloaded from and Select "Anywhere".
